  "summary": "Malicious code in workbox-stable-xyz (npm)",
  "details": "Workbox-stable-xyz@1.0.0 is a combosquat package impersonating Google's workbox library. On installation the preinstall script (node index.js) collects system information — hostname, home directory path, current username, DNS server addresses, and the installer's working directory — and POSTs the data as a URL-encoded HTTPS request to eo1jookr73gehju[.]m[.]pipedream[.]net. The destination is a Pipedream webhook endpoint, a common C2/exfiltration service. The collected metadata can be used to fingerprint the victim environment for follow-on targeting.",
